==English==

=== Adjective ===

'''temporal''' (''no comparative or superlative'')

# Of or relating to [[time]]
# Of [[limit]]ed [[time]]; not [[perpetual]]
# Of or relating to the material world; not spiritual;
#{{euphemistic}} [[last]]ing a [[short]] [[time]] only
# of the [[temple]]s of the head.

